1.title: Driving Starts, Stops, Stalls
1.plot: Elli's near miss during her first driving lesson. Teens turn the tables on the parents and ask 'Who is teaching the driving instructors?'

2.title: Driving Tests and Challenges
2.plot: A teen crash re-enactment starts as a bit of fun and takes an unexpected turn and we ask, 'Should the driving test be easier or harder?

3.title: Driving: Just Ask a Teen
3.plot: Teens vs Parents Road Safety Ad Competition gets serious but what has the teens completely forget about safety?

4.title: Driving: Who Needs Cars Anyway?
4.plot: They think they know best and hate being told what to do - and that's the parents - who get a chance to redeem themselves at Advanced Driving but - in the end - 'do we really NEED cars?'
